column34: Overall Survival: 1 if there was any evidence of tumor (visible, before necropsy or after IHC, behavior change or unexplained death), 0 if not
column35: Tumor Free Survival: 1 only if there was any abnormal mass or enlargement visible upon necropsy or H&E, 0 if mouse survived to 150 days and had no tumor, exclude if death was early and no hard proof of tumor
column36: Glioma Free Survival: 1 if a glioma (inside brain or infiltrating the brain, verified by Ki67), 0 if no observable glioma is present, exclude if H&E wasn't done or mouse was sacked before 150 days for whatever reason

column43: Auditory nerve? (Not connected to skull like head tumors, but on head and connected to skin sort of)
